      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-blue-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-4">Unusual 2-Letter Words: The Scrabble Trivia Corner</h2>

      <p>PO belongs to a category of 2-letter Scrabble words with surprisingly obscure meanings:</p>

