        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🏺 PO — Chamber Pot</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">From French "pot de chambre". Used in English since the 16th century. 4 points.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-cyan-500/30 bg-cyan-950/10">
          <p class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">🌊 KA — Egyptian Soul</p>
